text:
I see this tour as the last kind of shackles
being thrown off of being worried about what

I would love it if in 20 years I would look
back on this and think that's when I feel
like we started to become really good.

We don't tell anyone all the darker side of
things, we've been through all the break-ups

and addictions and all that, but you have
a chemistry that noone else in the world has.
So we don't mess with it.
